                        <h5>Double Rooms.</h5>
                        <h6>Equiped with fridge, tea/coffee stationary and kettle, iron and ironboard and more.</h6>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item" style="animation: fadein 1s;">
                    <img src="/imgs/rooms/1 (4).jpg" loading="lazy" class="d-block w-100 rounded" alt="Photo by Erik Mclean from Pexels" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.673);">
                        <h5>Single Rooms.</h5>
                        <h6>Not much different from double, only less space.</h6>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item" style="animation: fadein 1s;">
                    <img src="/imgs/spa/1 (4).jpg" loading="lazy" class="d-block w-100 rounded" alt="Photo by K HOWARD from Pexels" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.673);">
                        <h5>Vintage Cast Iron Bathtubs</h5>
                        <h6>Only the best for our guests.</h6>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item" style="animation: fadein 1s;">
                    <img src="/imgs/spa/1 (3).jpg" loading="lazy" class="d-block w-100 rounded" alt="Photo by K HOWARD from Pexels" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.673);">
                        <h5>Spa Time lover ?</h5>
                        <h6>No bookings necessary. Just come on and enjoy.</h6>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item" style="animation: fadein 1s;">
                    <img src="/imgs/other/1 (2).jpg" loading="lazy" class="d-block w-100 rounded" alt="Photo by K HOWARD from Pexels" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.673);">
                        <h5>Breakfast Buffet</h5>
                        <h6>Various choices on the breakfast buffet from all around the world.</h6>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
